"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/105851","HM Treasury","false","2014-11-10","<p>HM Treasury do not use iPhones and therefore have no associated spend since 2010.</p><p> </p>","South Northamptonshire","Andrea Leadsom",,"2014-11-10T17:48:47.5862233Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/105851/answer","Biography information for Andrea Leadsom","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/105851/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/105851/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","Treasury","2014-11-03","Mobile Phones","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how much his Department spent on iPhones in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for John Woodcock","Barrow and Furness","John Woodcock","213165"
