"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/106046","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-11-06","<p /> <p>Up to 30 June 2014, which was the date of the latest published staffing figures, there had been five or fewer prison officers who had taken voluntary early departure since 2010 and since returned to work for the National Offender Management Service.</p>","South West Bedfordshire","Andrew Selous",,"2014-11-06T16:24:45.9395581Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/106046/answer","Biography information for Andrew Selous","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/106046/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/106046/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-11-03","Prison Officers","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many prison officers who have taken voluntary early departure since 2010 have been re-recruited.","false","Biography information for Sadiq Khan","Tooting","Sadiq Khan","213133"
